sition section sits below the core fields in the Add Asset dialog and is shown for every type — Machine, Tooling, Facility, Vehicle, Other. It is independent of the Tooling-only fields below."}]},{"heading":"Tooling-Only Fields (shown when Type = Tooling)","items":[{"label":"Customer Owned","value":"Toggle switch. When ON, indicates the mold/tool belongs to a customer, not your shop. Affects reporting."},{"label":"Cavity Count","value":"Number input. For molds: how many cavities (parts per shot). Used in production planning."},{"label":"Tool Life Expectancy","value":"Number input. Expected total shots/cycles before the tool needs replacement. Compared against Current Shot Count."},{"label":"Current Shot Count","value":"Display only (in detail view). Current number of shots/cycles. When approaching Tool Life Expectancy, indicates tool is nearing end of life."},{"label":"Source Job","value":"Entity link (display only). The job that created this tooling asset. Clickable to open the job detail."},{"label":"Source Part","value":"Entity link (display only). The part this tooling produces. Clickable to open the part detail."}]},{"heading":"Asset Statuses","items":[{"label":"Active (green chip)","value":"Asset is in service and available for use. Default status for new assets."},{"label":"Maintenance (yellow chip)","value":"Asset is currently down for scheduled or unscheduled maintenance. Signals to the team that the machine is unavailable."},{"label":"Retired (gray chip)","value":"Asset has been permanently taken out of service. Record preserved for history and depreciation tracking."},{"label":"Out of Service (red chip)","value":"Asset is broken or otherwise unavailable. Different from Maintenance — indicates an unplanned outage."}]},{"heading":"Asset Types and Icons","items":[{"label":"Machine","value":"Icon: precision_manufacturing. Production equipment (CNC, lathe, saw, press)."},{"label":"Tooling","value":"Icon: build. Molds, dies, jigs, fixtures, cutting tools. Has extra fields for cavity count, shot count, and customer ownership."},{"label":"Facility","value":"Icon: apartment. Buildings, HVAC, electrical, infrastructure."},{"label":"Vehicle","value":"Icon: local_shipping. Delivery trucks, forklifts, company vehicles."},{"label":"Other","value":"Icon: category. Anything that doesn't fit the above categories."}]},{"heading":"Buttons and Actions","items":[{"label":"Add Asset (primary button)","value":"Opens the asset creation dialog. data-testid: new-asset-btn"},{"label":"Save (dialog)","value":"Creates or updates the asset. Disabled when form is invalid or save is in progress. data-testid: asset-save-btn"},{"label":"Cancel (dialog)","value":"Closes the dialog without saving."},{"label":"Edit (detail panel)","value":"Opens the edit dialog pre-filled with the asset's current values."},{"label":"Set Status buttons (detail)","value":"Quick-action buttons to change status to Active, Maintenance, Retired, or Out of Service directly from the detail panel."},{"label":"Row click","value":"Opens the asset detail panel/dialog showing all fields, tooling details, barcode info, and maintenance history."}]},{"heading":"Machine Operating Hours","items":[{"label":"Current Hours (table + detail)","value":"Running operating-hours total for the asset. Shown in the Current Hours table column (right-aligned, '—' when zero) and in the detail panel's Hours row. Display-only on those screens."},{"label":"How hours are updated","value":"Operating hours are updated via the machine-hours endpoint (PATCH /assets/{id}/hours), not by typing into the detail panel. Hours feed tool-life and maintenance-interval tracking. There is no free-text edit box for hours on the detail panel today — updates come from the hours action/integration."},{"label":"Why hours matter","value":"Rising hours are how usage-based maintenance intervals and (for tooling) tool-life comparisons advance. Keep them current so scheduled maintenance fires on time."}]},{"heading":"Validation Rules","items":[{"label":"Name","value":"Required. Cannot be empty."},{"label":"Type","value":"Required. Must select one of the five types."},{"label":"Acquisition Cost","value":"Optional, but if entered must be ≥ 0 and ≤ 1,000,000,000. Negative or out-of-range values block Save."},{"label":"All other fields","value":"Optional. No length or format restrictions beyond reasonable limits."},{"label":"Submit button popover","value":"When the form is invalid, the validation-button icon next to Save lists which fields need attention."}]},{"heading":"Table Columns","items":[{"label":"Icon","value":"Asset type icon. Not sortable."},{"label":"Name","value":"Sortable. Asset name text."},{"label":"Asset Type","value":"Sortable, filterable (enum). Machine/Tooling/Facility/Vehicle/Other."},{"label":"Location","value":"Sortable. Physical location text."},{"label":"Manufacturer","value":"Sortable. Equipment manufacturer."},{"label":"Status","value":"Sortable. Color-coded chip: Active (green), Maintenance (yellow), Retired (gray), Out of Service (red)."},{"label":"Current Hours","value":"Sortable, right-aligned. Operating hours tracked for the asset."}]}]}"""
